OL,6,FA mother whose son died after being
OL,7,Fstabbed is giving her backing to the
OL,8,Finstallation of new bleed kits across .
OL,10,FZoe Cooke's son Byron was stabbed
OL,11,Ftwice with a knife in July 2021.
OL,13,FSince then she has campaigned for more
OL,14,Fbleed kits to be available to help
OL,15,Fpeople carry out first aid while
OL,16,Fwaiting for paramedics to arrive.
OL,18,FShe's now been to see one installed at
OL,19,Fa construction site in Nottingham.
