OL,4,Cbacks bleed kits at construction sites
OL,6,FShe says: "These are saving lives.
OL,7,FLike up to twice a week these are
OL,8,Fbeing used.
OL,10,F"The more these are around the
OL,11,Fcountry, the more lives can be saved.
OL,12,FAnd I really take my hat off to them
OL,13,Ffor doing this."
OL,15,FIt's been five years since bleed
OL,16,Fcontrol kits were first introduced in
OL,17,FNottingham City Centre.
