OL,6,FTheir aim was to allow people giving
OL,7,Femergency 1st Aid vital time, while
OL,8,Fwaiting for paramedics to arrive. But
OL,9,Fnow their distribution and
OL,10,Finstallation is being expanded.
OL,12,FAt the construction site in the city,
OL,13,Fthe developer has had one of the kits
OL,14,Finstalled on its hoardings.
OL,16,FMike Dowson, managing director of
OL,17,FTurtle Engineering, the firm that
OL,18,Fmakes them, said: "You enter the code
OL,19,Fas you all know, And when you open it,
OL,20,Finside you've got the bleed control
OL,21,Fkit.
