OL,3,CMum whose son died after being stabbed
OL,4,Cbacks bleed kits at construction sites
OL,6,F"There's always this association that
OL,7,Fit's about stabbings, and about gangs,
OL,8,Fand that's really not the case.
OL,10,F"We see where these kits are being
OL,11,Fused all the time. And it's car
OL,12,Fcrashes in remote little villages
OL,13,Fwhere the ambulance is 45 minutes away.
OL,15,F"It's an industrial accident,
OL,16,Fsomething where's there's all the
OL,17,Fhealth & safety in place, but
OL,18,Faccidents happen."JThe bleed kits
OL,19,Fthemselves contain various pieces of
OL,20,Fequipment.
