OL,12,Fthis bleed kit, did it after hearing
OL,13,FZoe's story, and is hoping others will
OL,14,Ffollow suit.JRichard Hardy, health and
OL,15,Fsafety advisor for Graham Building and
OL,16,FDevelopments Limited, said: "The
OL,17,Fcompany first became aware of the
OL,18,Fcamapuign down in Birmingham.
