OL,6,F"It's something we'd like to back, and
OL,7,Fobviously we'd like to advise other
OL,8,Fcompanies to do the same thing.
OL,10,FMr Dowson said: "We hear from families
OL,11,Fand people who have been saved,
OL,12,Fregularly. And they're just so
OL,13,Fgrateful that the kit was there. That
OL,14,Fit was available when needed."JSince
OL,15,Fher sons death, Zoe Cooke's efforts to
OL,16,Fhave more bleed control kits installed
OL,17,Facross towns and cities, won her the
OL,18,FEast Midlands Pride of Britain Award
OL,19,Ffor fundraising.
